{
  "stem": "5371.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nebel. ?] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After a while, I got to know the civilian [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Germans who were ahead-- were at the head of the company, or the head of the section.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, they were always asking me if I have any gold, or dollars, or diamonds.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had-- I had access to it because of the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had access to all that thing, because they were sorting out all that money, the diamonds, everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, they had access to everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they were taken always with them to their quarters some, you know, because there was no accounting of what they found or what they had selected.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to get from them, and I used to give it to these Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave me-- they gave-- brought bread, cigarettes I smoked them also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cigarettes and sometimes salami.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the problem was to take it into camp, because when you walked into camp every day, every evening after work, there were a row of SS standing on each side and watching if you have no any-- no bulges, because stomachs nobody had, you know.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because from the food they give you, couldn't have no stomach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we used to hide it in our pants, tied down the pants or in the pants, you know, no big package, always small packages.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day I remember they were going through very thoroughly, you know, and I had on me some stuff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew they-- they gonna find it on me, because they were close to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I ran away at that time, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the-- the-- my luck was that a lot of people were already on that street who came back from work.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
